0.5.1
=====
 - Scrollbars now draggable
 - Container scrollbar areas no longer bubble events

0.5.0
=====
 - Changed events to now use binding with an event manager. This allows for one event to have an arbitrary number of callbacks associated with it.

0.4.5
=====
 - Added CHANGELOG, README and LICENSE
 - Added documentation
 - Added examples
 - Started naming versions. 0.4.5 sounds good.
